				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2008/12/12/505-ces-deputes-qui-nous-cassent-les-urnes?replytocom=4640#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-4640", "4640", "respond", "505")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
